# ethtool -i eth0 # will show current patch version

Download the nic driver details from citrix portal
1. copy the downloaded package on poolmaster
2. unzip the packages.
#excute the below command-
rpm -ivh bnx2x-1.714.6-1.src.rpm
mount -l bnx2x.iso /mnt
cd /mnt/
./install
depmod -a 'uname -r'
sh /boot/*cmd
then reboot & check driver verstion.
